OL,6,FCarla Ward is stepping down as Aston
OL,7,FVilla manager at the end of the season
OL,8,Fin what she described as the "hardest
OL,9,Fdecision" of her managerial career.
OL,11,FIt's after a tough campaign where
OL,12,FAston Villa Women have struggled to
OL,13,Freach the highs of the 2023 season,
OL,14,Fwhere Ward led them to a fifth-place
OL,15,Ffinish and a Women's FA Cup semi-final.
