OL,3,CCarla Ward to step down as Aston Villa
OL,4,Cmanager at end of season
OL,6,FWard, 40, joined Villa three years
OL,7,Fago. During her tenure, Villa have
OL,8,Fbrought in international players such
OL,9,Fas Rachel Corsie, Jordan Nobbs and
OL,10,Fcurrent PFA Women's Players' Player of
OL,11,Fthe Year Rachel Daly.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Ward said: "To step
OL,14,Fdown from my post here at Aston Villa
OL,15,Fhas been the hardest decision of my
OL,16,Fmanagerial career, but I know it is
OL,17,Fthe right one for my family and I.
