OL,3,CCarla Ward to step down as Aston Villa
OL,4,Cmanager at end of season
OL,6,F"Managing a great club like Aston
OL,7,FVilla has been a full-throttle job and
OL,8,FI have always given the role 100 per
OL,9,Fcent dedication. However, I now
OL,10,Fbelieve it is the right time for me to
OL,11,Fprioritise the other important things
OL,12,F- such as my daughter and the rest of
OL,13,Fmy family life."
OL,15,FMonchi, Villa's president of football
OL,16,Foperations, said: "Carla came to us a
OL,17,Ffew weeks ago and spoke of her plan to
OL,18,Fstep down.
