OL,3,CCarla Ward to step down as Aston Villa
OL,4,Cmanager at end of season
OL,6,F"We have had extensive dialogue with
OL,7,Fher to see if there was anything we
OL,8,Fcould do to persuade her to stay, but
OL,9,Fshe is adamant that she wants to take
OL,10,Fa break from the game."
OL,12,FThe news of Ward's stepping down will
OL,13,Fbe upsetting for Villa fans, despite
OL,14,Fher team coming under criticism for
OL,15,Fdrops in form this season. The highest
OL,16,Fposition Ward's Villa could finish on
OL,17,Fis sixth place, although that would
OL,18,Frely on Tottenham Hotspur women losing
OL,19,Ftheir remaining fixtures.
